    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong>, then combine the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1664348983950-x200.jpg",
