            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roll out each <strong>dough ball</strong> to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>floured</strong> <strong>rolling pin </strong>into a rough oval shape</p><p>Pinch and twist the ends of each oval to form a boat-shape – this is your <strong>pide base[s]</strong></p><p>Remove the baking tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>pide base[s] </strong>(be careful- the tray[s] will be hot!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
