      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>pide base[s]</strong> with the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>filling</strong></p><p>Crack one <strong>egg</strong> into each centre and sprinkle over your <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Drizzle the crusts with a little <strong>olive oil</strong>, then put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the crust has puffed up and browned – this is your <strong>cheesy harissa & spinach pide</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
