      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to the <strong>remaining quick-pickled red onion</strong> with the <strong>diced apricot </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>apricot salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>cheesy harissa & spinach pide </strong>topped with the <strong>remaining sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>apricot salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
